
   ABILITY:  trophy <body part>
   LEVEL:    Thug/Hitman
   COST:     Low graft

   DESCRIPTION:
     Take a body part from your victim's corpse as a trophy.  This
     is not just proof of a kill but also a tool to inspire fear.
     Trophies may be put on display in the family restaurant.
     Possible body parts are: head, arm, leg, hand, foot.

